text.section:
"Earnings" includes:
any form of periodic payment to an individual, including:
an annuity;
a pension;
Social Security payments;
workers' compensation payments; and
unemployment insurance benefits; and
any commissions or fees paid in connection with the obligor's employment.

"Support" includes:
child support;
spousal support;
support of destitute adult children; and
support of destitute parents.
